OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1950FThe first episode of Prudence
OL,7,FKitten airs on BBC TV.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1957FThe first edition of Criss Cross
OL,10,FQuiz airs on ITV.
OL,11,
OL,12,CG1962FThe first episode of Steptoe and
OL,13,FSon airs on BBC TV.
OL,14,
OL,15,FThis episode was a repeat of the Comedy
OL,16,FPlayhouse pilot, The Offer.
OL,17,
OL,18,FThe first new episode - The Bird - was
OL,19,Fbroadcast on 14th June 1962.
