OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1968FThe final edition of Whistle
OL,7,FStop airs on BBC One. Children's
OL,8,Fvariety show with musical guests.
OL,9,FHosted by Roger Whittaker.
OL,10,
OL,11,CG1971FBlue Peter famously buried a
OL,12,Ftime capsule, which was not to be
OL,13,Fopened until the year 2000.
OL,14,
OL,15,CG1973FThe first episode of Warship
OL,16,Fairs on BBC One. The drama series
OL,17,Ffollowed the adventures of the crew of
OL,18,Ffrigate HMS Hero.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG1981FThe final edition of Blue Peter
OL,21,FSpecial Assignment airs on BBC One.
