OL,5,
OL,6,CG1984FThe first edition of Crimewatch
OL,7,FUK airs on BBC One. Presented by Nick
OL,8,FRoss and Sue Cook. Radio Times: "The
OL,9,Ffirst in a new monthly series which
OL,10,Fasks you, the viewer, to turn
OL,11,Fdetective, crime-solver and
OL,12,Fcrime-preventer."
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1985FThe final episode of The
OL,15,FDetective airs on BBC One.
OL,16,
OL,17,FDramatised by Ted Whitehead from the
OL,18,Fnovel by Paul Ferris.
