OL,5,
OL,6,CG1996FThe final edition of Jeopardy!
OL,7,F(revived version) airs on Sky TV.
OL,8,
OL,9,FGame show. Hosted by Paul Ross. Based
OL,10,Fon the US version of the same title.
OL,11,
OL,12,FPrevious incarnations of the programme
OL,13,Faired on Channel 4 (1983 - 1984) and
OL,14,FITV (1990 - 1993). It was revived again
OL,15,Fby ITV in 2023.
OL,16,
OL,17,CG1997FThe first episode of The Other
OL,18,FHalf airs on BBC One.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG2004FThe first edition of The Gadget
OL,21,FShow airs on Channel 5.
